    <item>
      <title>毛伊岛火灾由电线断裂引起，县政府和美国政府发现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/maui-fire-caused-by-broken-utility-power-lines-report-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毛伊岛消防部门表示，去年，夏威夷电力工业公司重新接通断裂的公共设施线路时产生的火花点燃了未维护的干燥植被，从而引发了火灾，烧毁了毛伊岛历史悠久的拉海纳镇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/maui-fire-caused-by-broken-utility-power-lines-report-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 22:30:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
